  m_Name: LoopReflect_01
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ReflectBranch
  lines:
  - Okay, Luke.
  - Today is the day.
  - It's now or never.
  - No more chickening out.
  - She's right there at her locker.
  - "You\u2019re gonna walk right up to Daisy Winfield\u2026"
  - And you're gonna ask her to the Homecoming Dance.
  - "And if you DON\u2019T ask her this passing period\u2026"
  - Brett Kissinger is gonna ask her.
  - And they'll get married.
  - And you'll die ALONE.
  - "Just\u2026 ask her."
  commitLines:
  - "Bell\u2019s gonna ring soon."
  - "It\u2019s GO time."
  - "Deep breath\u2026"
  - You can do this.
